author: Caitlin  Yilek
title: House blocks GOP Rep. Nancy Mace's censure effort against fellow Republican Cory Mills - CBS News
description: The Florida congressman has faced a number of controversies this year, ranging from alleged assault and harassment to stolen valor and federal contracting violations. He has denied any wrongdoing.
content: Washington — The House blocked an effort to formally censure Republican Rep. Cory Mills of Florida and strip him of his committee assignments over allegations related to federal contracting violation… [+3471 chars]
